data.description: Don't miss this fully renovated showcase in the sought-after Westwood Terrace neighborhood! This beautifully designed residence offers an impeccable floorplan, providing ample living space. With a blend of modern features and timeless charm, this property exudes sophistication and elegance. Finished with hardwoods throughout the main floor and a top-of-the-line appliance package, this kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's dream. The oversized island serves as the centerpiece for social gatherings or food prep.  The keeping room and main-level bedroom i are truly exceptional features that add functionality and convenience to the home. The keeping room provides a versatile space for relaxation or informal gatherings, . Meanwhile, the main-level bedroom offers a private retreat for guest or the perfect sun lit home office. These thoughtful additions elevate the overall livability of the home and make it a truly desirable and practical choice for modern living.   The location of this property is equally impressive. A mere 0.3 mile walk away from the SW Connector Trail on the Beltline, you'll have direct access to nature's beauty and recreational activities. Enjoy leisurely walks or bike rides amidst serene surroundings. Additionally, you'll be minutes away from the renowned John E. White Golf Course, Draft House, Mon Night Brewery, and the trendy Lee+White Development, ensuring an abundance of entertainment options.  Special financing is available. Seller LOVES the home and area but is being recruited to another state. ***$10,000 seller credit toward closing cost or rate buydown with acceptable offer***
